    <item>
      <title>Task Management System</title>
      <link>https://010101-sans.github.io/projects/task-management-system/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:20:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://010101-sans.github.io/projects/task-management-system/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A collaborative task management web application for teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real-time collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Task assignment and tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team workspaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Activity timeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple view options (list, board, timeline)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;tech-stack&#34;&gt;Tech Stack&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend&lt;/strong&gt;: React with TypeScript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend&lt;/strong&gt;: Node.js + Express&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Database&lt;/strong&gt;: PostgreSQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real-time&lt;/strong&gt;: WebSockets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;results&#34;&gt;Results&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Used by 500+ teams managing 100,000+ tasks monthly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
